node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sour Patch Kids on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, candy and text that says 'SOUR THENSWEET. SOUR PATCH ads #%1& OuT oF WoRk SaUtE CoOK 7/22 @ChefRykard Who knew they had tropical sour patch kids'.

Photo by Sour Patch Kids on July 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HELLO SOUR PATCH KIDS SPIES HERE IS YOUR FINAL CLUE: ACROSS THE POND IT HAS A DIFFERENT NAME BUT THERE'S AN EXTRA INGREDIENT IN THE GAME YOU HAVE UNTIL 8/15 TO SOLVE THE CLUES AND FIGURE OUT THE FLAVOR, OR RISK THE OTHER KIDS AT THE PATCH LOSING THEIR FLAVORS TOO BEST OF LUCK, PATCH HO THIS MESSAGE WILL SELF DESTRUCT'.

node.text:
Here it is, your final clue from PATCH HQ. Have you solved the mystery? Are you almost there? No time like right now to make your guess via the link in bio!

50 U.S., D.C. & PR 13+. Ends: 8/15/21. Void where prohibited. Rules & free entry: http://sourpatchkidsmystery.com.
